OL,3,CVoters charged #5 to open candidate's
OL,4,Celection letters
OL,6,FPeople sent letters by a general
OL,7,Felection candidate who failed to put
OL,8,Fstamps on them have had to foot the
OL,9,Fbill for his error.
OL,11,FJonathan Bishop, who was standing as
OL,12,Fan independent in Pontypridd, has cost
OL,13,Fsome voters #5 to open his election
OL,14,Fcampaign letters.
OL,16,FMr Bishop is thought to have not put
OL,17,Fstamps on 98 of the letters he sent
OL,18,Fout.
