OL,3,CVoters charged #5 to open candidate's
OL,4,Celection letters
OL,6,FResidents in the area were then
OL,7,Fcontacted by Royal Mail and told they
OL,8,Fhad an outsanding balance to pay to
OL,9,Fcollect the mail, without any
OL,10,Findication of what it was.
OL,12,FA spokesman for Royal Mail said any
OL,13,Fclaims for refunds should be directed
OL,14,Fto the person who sent the letters.
OL,16,FHeledd Fychan MS was one of those who
OL,17,Freceived the letter and paid the #5.
