OL,6,FShe raised the issue in the Senedd on
OL,7,FTuesday 9 July, and said she had
OL,8,Fcontacted the candidate to ask about
OL,9,Frefunds.
OL,11,FIn a response to her Mr Bishop wrote:
OL,12,F"Royal Mail and The Crocels Press
OL,13,FLimited have taken part in an
OL,14,Finvestigation into this matter and
OL,15,Fidentified up to 98 people could be
OL,16,Faffected.
