OL,3,CVoters charged #5 to open candidate's
OL,4,Celection letters
OL,6,F"The names and addresses of those 98
OL,7,Fpeople have been supplied to Royal
OL,8,FMail who will: deliver without charge
OL,9,Fto those who have not paid; refund
OL,10,Fthose who have paid. Royal Mail and
OL,11,FThe Crocels Press Limited have
OL,12,Fapologised for the situation and
OL,13,Flessons will be learned."
OL,15,FCrocels Press Limited is a company
OL,16,Flisted on Companies House with Mr
OL,17,FBishop as its sole director.
