OL,3,CVoters charged #5 to open candidate's
OL,4,Celection letters
OL,6,FIn the letter to Ms Fychan it says
OL,7,Fthose affected should contact The
OL,8,FCrocels Press Limited on
OL,9,Fbriefs@crocels.net for more
OL,10,Finformation.
OL,12,FSpeaking afterwards Ms Fychan said:
OL,13,F"Clearly something went very wrong and
OL,14,Fit's imperative now that everyone that
OL,15,Fpaid #5 to receive the election
OL,16,Fcommunication is refunded.
OL,18,F"Constituents paid thinking it was an
OL,19,Fimportant letter and were rightly
OL,20,Fangry when they found out what they
OL,21,Fpaid for."
